{"tid":1800370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左中文維基百科，英文維基百科都係重要戰線，有勞手足翻譯。","createTime":"2019-12-27T17:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T18:04:35.000Z","uid":89937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba67fca21b03ccaa36bf123a511daca0802a672a","tid":1800370,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"英文維基百科往往係鬼佬認識發生乜野事好重要既一環。有D條目o係中文版資料其實OK齊料，但英文版就好少料。所以希望大家幫手將同反送中有關既條目，中文版翻譯到英文版，或者加料落英文版。<br />\n只要你o係任何一個Wikipedia有戶口，o係英文維基百科都有得。<br />\n(兩個版本都要有一定資料來源支持，創建新條目既規定方面，兩個語言版本有一定差別，所以暫時不談。)<br />\n<br />\n其實有好多，熟左手大家會好快OK，大家加油。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stand_News\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FStand_News&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=4584584e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stand_News</a><br />\n<br />\n樂翠(何君堯原任選區)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A8%82%E7%BF%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25A8%2582%25E7%25BF%25A0&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=faf23cb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%A8%82%E7%BF%A0</a><br />\n<br />\n何君堯<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Junius_Ho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FJunius_Ho&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=a6f76883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Junius_Ho</a><br />\n<br />\n吳秋北<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ng_Chau-pei\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNg_Chau-pei&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=0ed1cb23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ng_Chau-pei</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"